Package paint.shared.io

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseTableIO
    Abstract base class for consistent CSV and Table I/O across the PAINT modules.
    ExperimentDataLoader
    Provides centralized functionality for loading all experiment-related data: recordings, tracks, and (for mature projects) squares.
    ExperimentInfoTableIO
    Provides table input/output utilities for ExperimentInfo records (per-recording metadata).
    HelperIO
    Utility class providing static helper methods for reading and writing Recording, Square, and Track data in a PAINT experiment directory.
    RecordingTableIO
    Provides table I/O utilities for Recording entities.
    SquareTableIO
    Provides all CSV input/output operations for Square entities.
    TrackTableIO
    Provides CSV I/O and schema enforcement for Track entities.
